#. Tag: date
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "2003-03-08"
msgstr "8 de març de 2003"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"

# skip-rule: punctuation-period-no
#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "fool <command>make</command> into not rebuilding certain files"
msgstr ""
"enganya a <command>make</command> perquè no reconstrueixi certs fitxers."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>cheatmake</command> <group><option>hidechange</option> "
"<replaceable>file</replaceable></group> <group><option>show</option></group> "
"<group><option>why</option> <replaceable>file</replaceable></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>cheatmake</command> <group><option>hidechange</option> "
"<replaceable>fitxer</replaceable></group> <group><option>show</option></"
"group> <group><option>why</option> <replaceable>fitxer</replaceable></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripció"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>cheatmake</command> is used to save time when recompiling. It can "
"fool make into skipping files that haven't changed in a meaningful way. This "
"can be used for instance when you change a comment in a file but none of the "
"actual code."
msgstr ""
"L'ordre <command>cheatmake</command> s'usa per a estalviar temps durant les "
"recompilacions. Podeu enganyar a «make» perquè passi per alt els fitxers amb "
"modificacions que no tinguin importància com per exemple quan afegiu "
"comentaris al codi real."

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta utilitat forma part del joc de desenvolupament de programari del "
"&kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcions"

#. Tag: term
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>hidechange</option> <replaceable>file</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>hidechange</option> <replaceable>fitxer</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hides the fact that file was changed by setting the timestamp into the past. "
"Use with care!"
msgstr ""
"Ocult el fet que el fitxer ha canviat establint la marca de temps en un "
"moment anterior. Empreu-ho amb cura!"

#. Tag: option
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "show"
msgstr "show"

# skip-rule: punctuation-period-no
#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists what files <command>make</command> currently needs to rebuild"
msgstr "Llista quins fitxers necessitarà reconstruir <command>make</command>."

#. Tag: term
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>why</option> <replaceable>file</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>why</option> <replaceable>fitxer</replaceable>"

# skip-rule: punctuation-period-no
#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Explains why make must rebuild file"
msgstr ""
"Explica la raó per la qual «make» necessita reconstruir un determinat fitxer."

#. Tag: title
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment"
msgstr "Entorn"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the following variables (but not both) should be set if the source "
"directory is different from the build directory. If the build directory is "
"simply a subdirectory of the source directory, the simpler variable "
"<envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> should be used."
msgstr ""
"Hauria de configurar-se una de les variables següents (però no ambdues) si "
"el directori font és diferent del que realitzareu la compilació. Si el "
"directori de compilació és un subdirectori dintre del codi font, haureu "
"d'usar la variable <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar>."

#. Tag: envar
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_SUBJDIR"
msgstr "OBJ_SUBJDIR"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Indicates that the build directory is in the given subdirectory of the "
"source directory. For instance, if the source directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> and the build directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, then <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</"
"envar> should be set to <parameter>obj-i386-linux</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"Indica que el directori de compilació està en un subdirectori a dins del "
"codi font. Per exemple, si el directori del codi font és <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> i el de compilació <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, aleshores <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</"
"envar> haurà d'estar establerta a <parameter>obj-i386-linux</parameter>."

#. Tag: envar
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_REPLACEMENT"
msgstr "OBJ_REPLACEMENT"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <command>sed</command> expression that is used to transform the source "
"directory into the build directory. For instance, if the source directory is "
"<filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, then "
"<envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</envar> should be set to <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk-"
"obj#</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"Per a transformar el directori del codi font en el de compilació s'empra una "
"expressió de <command>sed</command>. Per exemple, si el directori de les "
"fonts és <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, "
"aleshores <envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</envar> hauria d'estar establert a "
"<parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk-obj#</parameter>."

